      "date": "2015-06-29 04:16:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/f5687432-1e14-11e5-ade2-5254006e85c2).  Ran 17 tests.  No failures.",
