      "date": "2015-06-29 14:33:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Code-Review+2\n\nI think this patch is good.\n\nWe need some serious interop testing.\nIn particular we need to make sure that:\nbulk resend works with old clent, new server and new server,old client.\nAlso we need to check the same for EInPROGRESS-induced resends.\n\nOne more thing, we probably want an assertion (As a separate testing patch not for final landing, but just to ensure no omissions were present) that if the compat flag IS set, to make sure that when RESENT flag is set, xid is not equal to matchbits",
